These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, montecristo, ritmeester
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, tram, motorbike
City: san-francisco, hannover, marseilles
3 different games are played: canasta, billiard, scrabble
1. the person driving the tram is the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the taxi is in the middle##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Cigar      | ritmeester  | davidoff       | montecristo   |
| Transport          | motorbike | taxi | tram |
| City         | san-francisco  | marseilles | hannover    |
| Game   | scrabble | canasta       | billiard      |

