.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
City: new-york, london, nizza
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, amaryllis
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, siglo, swisher
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, animation, family
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| City          | new-york      | london  | nizza        |
| Flower         | amaryllis | tulip | sunflower |
| Cigar   | vegafina | siglo | swisher       |
| Movie-Genre           | family     | animation     | martial-arts      |

