.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour, surfing
There are 3 different nationalities: german, russian, canadian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, house, reggae
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, aconite, daisy
1. the canadian is the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the russian is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Sport      | parkour    | snowboarding        | surfing |
| Nationality           | russian    | canadian | german    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | reggae             | house  |
| Flower     | daisy     | dahlia                | aconite  |

