House: art-deco, victorian, gothic-revival
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, scrabble, backgammon
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, lily
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the victorian house##1
2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the argentine##1
3. the gothic-revival house is the italian##1
4. the italian is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is the argentine##1
6. the person playing backgammon is the art-deco house##1
7. the victorian house is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Nationality         | italian | argentine     | french   |
| House           | gothic-revival       | victorian   | art-deco     |
| Game   | scrabble     | mah-jongg | backgammon |
| Flower           | lily      | begonia         | sunflower  |

