.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, october
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, photographer, chef
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, filmmaking, singing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, oliveros, montecristo
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in the middle##1
3. the chef is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Birthday          | february | august       | october |
| Job   | chef     | paramedic       | photographer   |
| Hobby           | filmmaking      | reading       | singing     |
| Cigar         | aristoff   | oliveros | montecristo  |

