3. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
