The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, firefighter, chef
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, orchid
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, avocado, pumpkin
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsorchid is the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the havana-smoker is in the middle##1
4. the chef is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the firefighter##1
6. the person eating cauliflower is the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
