2. the person who likes black is on the far right##1
3. the havana-smoker is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the far left##1
6. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar       | havana            | tiparillo      | davidoff  |
| Food         | pineapple | asparagus | apricot |
| Color         | pink               | lavender | black |
| Flower   | balloon-flower             | azalea       | daffodil      |

