There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, 7up
There 3 different types of food: mango, pomegranate, apple
City: nizza, boston, hamburg
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person traveling to boston##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the colonial house is on the far right##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person eating apple##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| House           | craftsman | cape-cod         | colonial |
| Beverage   | milk      | hot-chocolate | 7up     |
| Food   | mango   | pomegranate       | apple     |
| City           | hamburg    | boston         | nizza        |

