.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: chestnut, blue, aquamarine
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, marigold, daisy
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, rat, mouse
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, card-games
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Color           | blue | aquamarine | chestnut |
| Flower   | daisy        | marigold       | bellflower     |
| Pet   | rat     | mouse         | rabbit     |
| Hobby     | card-games | rock-climbing          | filmmaking      |

