.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving, collecting
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, november, march
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, blue, ebony
There 3 different types of food: pear, asparagus, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3      |
| Hobby      | collecting    | skydiving | board-games |
| Birthday   | november | september     | march     |
| Color   | ebony        | blue        | black        |
| Food           | asparagus    | zucchini         | pear     |

