There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, mexican, malaysian
There 3 different types of food: papaya, potato, broccoli
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, iris, rose
1. the person who growsrose is the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is the mexican##1
5. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
6. the malaysian is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre         | drama | thriller | superhero   |
| Nationality           | malaysian     | nigerian    | mexican   |
| Food   | potato         | broccoli    | papaya   |
| Flower         | iris       | rose | poppy |

