3. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| House      | gothic-revival  | farmhouse   | townhouse  |
| Sport          | cycling   | handball | skateboarding   |
| Transport   | bike      | tram      | car    |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | bongani    | cain |

