.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, french, mexican
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, modern
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, pilot, doctor
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, western
1. the mexican is on the far left##1
2. the modern house is on the left of the indian##1
3. the doctor is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
6. the townhouse house is on the left of the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality          | mexican     | french    | indian    |
| House         | townhouse | modern | gothic-revival     |
| Job   | fisherman  | pilot      | doctor        |
| Movie-Genre         | animation   | zombie   | western |

 